Requires  the http://code.google.com/p/wordpress-library/[Python
Wordpress library].  To download and install:

  $ svn co http://wordpress-library.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ wordpress-library
  $ cd wordpress-library
  $ sudo python setup.py install
